output.sankey_title: Industry of graduate employment for 2012/13 academic year graduates of Agriculture, food and related studies one, three and five years after graduation (YAG), male Level 8 graduates from English HEIs, APs and FECs, 2018/19 tax year.
output.sankeytext1:
For  male ,  Level 8  graduates who studied Agriculture, food and related studies , the industry with the highest
                      proportion of graduates one year after graduation is  Education  ( 69.6 %), and at five years after graduation it is  Professional, scientific and technical activities  ( 39.5 %).
output.sankeytext2:
The most movement between one and three years after graduation is seen for Education, where 3,165 graduates move to Professional, scientific and technical activities. Between three and five
                       years after graduation it's seen for Professional, scientific and technical activities where2,315 graduates moved to Other.
